The Dark Frontier Blender Cheat Sheet
Version 1.0

This will grow as we learn Blender. I only want to include shortcuts we'll actually use for The Dark Frontier.

Navigation
Shortcut	Action
Middle Mouse	Rotate View
Shift + Middle Mouse	Pan
Mouse Wheel	Zoom
Numpad .	Frame Selected
Alt + Z	X-Ray Mode
Selection
Shortcut	Action
A	Select All
Alt + A	Deselect All
B	Box Select
C	Circle Select
Modes
Shortcut	Action
Tab	Object / Edit Mode
1	Vertex Select
2	Edge Select
3	Face Select
Transform
Shortcut	Action
G	Move (Grab)
G X	Move on X
G Y	Move on Y
G Z	Move on Z
S	Scale
S X	Scale X
S Y	Scale Y
S Z	Scale Z
R	Rotate
Modeling
Shortcut	Action
E	Extrude
Ctrl + B	Bevel
Ctrl + R	Loop Cut
I	Inset Face
K	Knife Tool
Object Creation
Shortcut	Action
Shift + A	Add Object
Shift + D	Duplicate
X	Delete
Apply
Shortcut	Action
Ctrl + A	Apply Menu
Ctrl + A → Scale	Apply Scale
Ctrl + A → Rotation	Apply Rotation
Undo
Shortcut	Action
Ctrl + Z	Undo
Ctrl + Shift + Z	Redo
Helpful
Shortcut	Action
N	Toggle Item Panel
F9	Adjust Last Operation
Ctrl + S	Save
Ctrl + Shift + S	Save As
