Blender Tricks We've Learned
Right-click after Loop Cut

Leaves the cut exactly where Blender previewed it.

Mouse Wheel during Bevel

Changes the number of segments.

F9

Brings back the settings for the last tool you used.

Dimensions > Scale

Always edit Dimensions when creating a new asset.

Only use Scale temporarily.

Then Apply Scale.